metadata.description:
WEPAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA

this is realidad from scorchy scorch x remcycles. song is about opening up the heart to your personal power and standing loud and proud in it. finding grace within despite all the negative that you have been through and taking leaps of faith for all your goals.

we intend to finish this song and create a music video to it during NFTLA since me and scorch will be together so we are very excited to share it with you all and find some new beautiful connections along the way! ENJOY!!!
